name: Multiverse Finance
description: Multiverse Finance is a complete DEFI ecosystem that will serve the different markets and industries. It leverages on the Binance Smart Chain which allow users to get the best of both worlds - the fast transaction processing and the smart contract functionality. DEX, staking, farming, lending, payments, and even NFT transactions are some of the key features that can be experienced by users, traders, and investors within the ecosystem.
